        " «يُومِئُ إِيمَاءً بِرَأْسِهِ عَنْ كُلِّ صَلاَةٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1055 - Layth al-Muradi asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a man who suffers from continuous nosebleeds from the time of the sun's zenith until nightfall.\nImam (as) replied: \"He should gesture with his head for each prayer.\""
        ]
